s, particularly in the elderly and those with underlying organic brain disease, who tend to be more sensitive to the central anticholinergic effects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/3521/', '', 'Cabergoline', 'Ketotifen, Levocetirizine, Trimethobenzamide, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 1767369485);
