ects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/3596/', '', 'Methdilazine, Azatadine, Ketotifen, Alimemazine, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Phenindamine, Desloratadine, Tripelennamine, Azelastine, Cyclizine, More', 'Ketotifen, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Chlorpheniramine, Azelastine, Terfenadine, Astemizole', 1767369485);
